---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Mit Freuden";
const description =
  "What brings joy to life? That's right: it's really, really well-made software. We think so too.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} locale="en">
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12 text-zinc-800">
    <div class="mb-20 lg:mb-24">
      <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <h1
          class="text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-zinc-900 lg:text-6xl"
        >
          Mit Freuden
        </h1>
        <svg
          class="h-16 lg:h-24"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 40 40"
        >
          <!-- Square Brackets [ ] - happy eyes ^^ -->
          <g>
            <path
              d="M 10 4 L 4 4 L 4 36 L 10 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 30 4 L 36 4 L 36 36 L 30 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 10 24 Q 20 32 30 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 12 18 Q 14 15 16 18"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
            <path
              d="M 24 18 Q 26 15 28 18"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="font-serif text-xl/8 lg:text-2xl/10">
        What brings joy to life? That's right: it's really, <span class="italic"
          >really</span
        > well-made software.
        <span class="mt-2 block italic lg:mt-3"> We think so too.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl leading-9 tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl">
        Complete solutions that deliver on their promises
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-lg/8 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        We develop
        <span class="font-bold">complete, ready-to-use software</span> together with
        you – from the initial idea to smooth production operation. Our solutions
        are web-based and run on all platforms. Including native mobile apps for
        iOS and Android if needed. This way you reach your users everywhere, without
        compromising on performance or user experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl leading-9 tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl">
        Software that brings joy
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-lg/8 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        What good is the best technology if nobody enjoys working with it?
        Really, really good software must not only function, it should also <span
          class="font-bold">bring joy</span
        >. That's why we focus on intuitive usability and design that not only
        looks good, but enables simple and functional operation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl leading-9 tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl">
        Experience that moves industries
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-lg/8 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        Our team has implemented projects in the most diverse sectors – from <span
          class="font-bold">retail to energy to warehouse logistics</span
        >. Every industry has its own challenges, and we know how to master
        them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl leading-9 tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl">
        Future-proof through proven technology
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-lg/8 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        We rely on <span class="font-bold">proven, future-proof</span> technologies
        that grow with your business. Our focus is on B2B solutions such as workflow
        automation, data visualization, or complex logistics systems that have been
        successfully deployed for years. We deliver software not only quickly and
        securely, but also scalably – from startups to enterprise solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl leading-9 tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl">
        We are reliable partners
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-lg/8 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        For us, software development is more than just writing code. We <span
          class="font-bold">live your projects</span
        > with you, understand your goals, and develop solutions that truly fit you.
        No standard packages, no half measures. Custom-built software that advances
        your business and brings you and your team joy day after day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-30 mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2
        class="mb-5 text-4xl leading-9 font-normal tracking-tight md:mb-5 md:text-4xl"
      >
        Sounds good?
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-2 max-w-2xl font-serif text-2xl/10 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        Then let's talk. We look forward to <span class="italic">your</span> project.
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-2xl/10 text-pretty md:max-w-3xl">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@mitfreuden.com"
          class="underline underline-offset-3 transition-all hover:text-amber-800/60"
          >Say hello</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
